ResourceHeader.ResourceName: SOLO Radio and Plasma Wave, Low Frequency Receiver (RPW-LFR) Basic Parameters Set 2, Survey Mode, Level 2 (L2), Data

RevisionEvent.Note: Initial release of metadata, ADAPT generated, LFB

ResourceHeader.Description: This file contains RPW LFR level 2R Survey BP2 data of the current test.
ResourceHeader.Acknowledgement: The authors are pleased to acknowledge the Solar Orbiter/RPW Investigation (M. Maksimovic, PIs) for access to data.. Data provided are Publicly available. If used in presentations or publications, please acknowledge Solar Orbiter/RPW Investigation (M. Maksimovic, PIs). Please read carefully the caveats attached to the data. For reporting purposes, we request bibliography information for any publication, etc., using these data. Please send information on the use of this data to: M. Maksimovic (PI).

Parameter.Caveats: Index to indicate the sampling frequency of the snapshot : F0, F1 or F2 in order to use only one skeleton for the 3 normal mode BP2 products of ICD.

Parameter.Set: Time series defined by using: Epoch_N_F0
Parameter.Description:
All the real part of the 5x5 calibrated matrices for all bins of F0 sampling frequency in normal mode in the SCM B1-B2-B3 axis system frame [no plot].
* Column 1 Labels from N_F0: [ 1968.00, 2736.00, 3504.00, 4272.00, 5040.00, 5808.00, 6576.00, 7344.00, 8112.00, 8880.00, 9648.00]. * Column 2 Labels from I5_DEP2: [ 0, 1, 2, 3, 4]. * Column 3 Labels from I5_DEP3: [ 0, 1, 2, 3, 4].

Parameter.Name: Epoch
Parameter.Description: Default time
Parameter.Caveats: * Primary time used as a reference in the file. This Parameter exhibits an increasing Monotonic Progression

Parameter.Name: QUALITY_FLAG
Parameter.Set: Time series defined by using: Epoch
Parameter.Description: Quality flag
Parameter.Caveats: Flag to indicate the quality of the data

Parameter.Name: QUALITY_BITMASK
Parameter.Set: Time series defined by using: Epoch
Parameter.Description: Bitmask flag
Parameter.Caveats: Flag to indicate any context information or status at the receiver or experiment level

Parameter.Name: COMMON_BIA_STATUS_FLAG
Parameter.Set: Time series defined by using: Epoch
Parameter.Description: LFR common parameters and BIAS status info relevancy flag
Parameter.Caveats: Flag to indicate the relevancy of LFR common parameters (SP0/1, R0/1/2, BW) and BIAS STATUS INFO which can be non representative for the first packet following a change in those parameters.

Parameter.Name: SURVEY_MODE
Parameter.Set: Time series defined by using: Epoch
Parameter.Description: LFR survey mode (0 for normal mode, 1 for burst mode)
Parameter.Caveats: Flag to indicate if the receiver in the SURVEY_BURST (=1) or SURVEY_NORMAL (=0) mode

Parameter.Name: Sampling frequency of the BP2
Parameter.Set: Time series defined by using: Epoch
Parameter.Description: Sampling frequency of the BP2
Parameter.Caveats: Index to indicate the sampling frequency of the BP2 : F0, F1 or F2 in order to use only one skeleton for the 3 normal mode bp2 products of ICD.

Parameter.Name: BIAS multiplexer setting
Parameter.Set: Time series defined by using: Epoch
Parameter.Description: Copy of multiplexer setting.
Parameter.Caveats: Indicates the mode of BIAS multiplexer for a set of BP2 parameters. Possible values are 0 : Standard operation. 1 : Probe 1 fails. 2 : Probe 2 fails. 3 : Probe 3 fails. 4 : Calibration mode 0. 5 : Calibration mode 1. 6 : Calibration mode 2. 7 : Calibration mode 3.

Parameter.Name: BIAS high voltage status
Parameter.Set: Time series defined by using: Epoch
Parameter.Description: Copy of enable/disable HV (+- 100V).
Parameter.Caveats: Indicates the status of BIAS HV. Possible values are DISABLED = 0. ENABLED = 1.

Parameter.Name: BIAS probe 1 status
Parameter.Set: Time series defined by using: Epoch
Parameter.Description: Copy of enable/disable BIAS 1.
Parameter.Caveats: Indicates the status of BIAS probe 1. Possible values are DISABLED = 0. ENABLED = 1.

Parameter.Name: BIAS probe 2 status
Parameter.Set: Time series defined by using: Epoch
Parameter.Description: Copy of enable/disable BIAS 2.
Parameter.Caveats: Indicates the status of BIAS probe 2. Possible values are DISABLED = 0. ENABLED = 1.

Parameter.Name: BIAS probe 3 status
Parameter.Set: Time series defined by using: Epoch
Parameter.Description: Copy of enable/disable BIAS 3.
Parameter.Caveats: Indicates the status of BIAS probe 3. Possible values are DISABLED = 0. ENABLED = 1.

Parameter.Name: BIAS status
Parameter.Set: Time series defined by using: Epoch
Parameter.Description: Copy of BIAS status.
Parameter.Caveats: Indicates the status of BIAS. Possible values are OFF = 0 - Power line off. ON = 1 - Power line on.

Parameter.Name: BIAS Works/BIAS Fails configuration.
Parameter.Set: Time series defined by using: Epoch
Parameter.Description: BIAS Works/BIAS Fails configuration.

Parameter.Name: Shaping of electrical data parameter 0.
Parameter.Set: Time series defined by using: Epoch
Parameter.Description: Shaping of electrical data.

Parameter.Name: Shaping of electrical data parameter 1.
Parameter.Set: Time series defined by using: Epoch
Parameter.Description: Shaping of electrical data.

Parameter.Name: Rooting of electrical data for F0.
Parameter.Set: Time series defined by using: Epoch
Parameter.Description: Rooting of electrical data.

Parameter.Name: Rooting of electrical data for F1.
Parameter.Set: Time series defined by using: Epoch
Parameter.Description: Rooting of electrical data.

Parameter.Name: Rooting of electrical data for F2.
Parameter.Set: Time series defined by using: Epoch
Parameter.Description: Rooting of electrical data.

Parameter.Name: CCSDS CUC format LFR time, coarse and fine parts
Parameter.Set: Time series defined by using: Epoch
Parameter.Description: Number of BP2 sets read for a given sampling frequency(F0, F1 or F2).
Parameter.Caveats: This indicates how many sets of BP1 have been read. Expected numbers for NORMAL MODE are 11 for F0, 13 for F1 and 12 for F2. Expected numbers for BURST MODE are 22 for F0 and 26 for F1.

Parameter.Name: Spaceraft Elapsed Time
Parameter.Set: Time series defined by using: Epoch
Parameter.Description: Elapsed Time of the onboard clock
Parameter.Caveats: * Spaceraft Elapsed Time This Parameter exhibits an increasing Monotonic Progression

Parameter.Name: SYNCHRO_FLAG
Parameter.Set: Time series defined by using: Epoch
Parameter.Description: Time synchronisation flag
Parameter.Caveats: Flag to indicate if the local time is synchronized with the RPW DPU clock or not. Possible values: synchronized=0, not synchronized=1. This flag is extracted from ACQUISITION_TIME in L0 packets, it is the MSB of the CUC time.

Parameter.Name: I5_Dep2
Parameter.Description: Index of 5 numbers to support listing

Parameter.Name: I5_Dep3
Parameter.Description: Index of 5 numbers to support listing
